      "description": "Affordable and dependable transportation for the value-minded buyer. This vehicle shows its age cosmetically, but it still offers solid everyday usefulness and a chance to get on the road without stretching your budget. A practical choice for a commuter, first-time driver, or anyone looking for inexpensive wheels with room to make it their own.",
