    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with some life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for someone who wants inexpensive transportation, a handy backup vehicle, or a fun little project. It shows its age and has its share of cosmetic and mechanical needs, but that\u2019s exactly why it\u2019s priced to move. If you\u2019re practical, handy, or just want something cheap to get started with, this could be a great fit. Come take a look and see if it\u2019s the right one for you.",
      "price": 4950.0,
