      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget runabout with strong enthusiast potential. Starts, runs, and moves, with an engine that pulls cleanly and a drivetrain that feels usable for someone looking for an affordable fixer-upper. Suspension, braking, and cosmetics show age, so expect the usual TLC and deferred maintenance that comes with a car in this category, but the bones are there for the right buyer. Great candidate for a daily beater, weekend wrenching project, or parts donor depending on your plans. Priced to sell and worth a look if you want something inexpensive with real upside.",
      "price": 5950.0,
