      "description": "This car has the kind of presence that turns an ordinary drive into a story. It carries a lived-in character that gives it real personality, with a classic, honest feel that\u2019s increasingly hard to find. Perfect for someone who sees potential where others just see age, it\u2019s a great fit as a budget-friendly daily, a hands-on project, or a spare set of wheels with soul. If you want something with charm, purpose, and plenty of opportunity to make it your own, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
