      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s seen some life but still has plenty to offer the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s a budget-friendly option for someone who wants affordable wheels, a project, or a handy runabout. Priced fairly for what it is, and sold with a straightforward, no-nonsense approach. If you\u2019re after cheap transport with potential, this could be a great fit.",
